{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6c43859d95","title":"视察河南时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"19df58432e","index":0,"year":1967,"month":9,"day":22,"articleId":"6c43859d95"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9a50528209","name":"纪登奎","type":"人物"},{"id":"9e41d5677c","name":"河南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/50-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji50":{"comments":[{"id":"950dcc4885","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1967年9月22日，毛泽东视察了河南“无产阶级文化大革命”，接见了刘建勋、王新、纪登奎，陪同接见的有杨成武、张春桥。这是刘建勋1967年9月26日传达的毛泽东的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e64d247af3","type":"title","text":"视察河南时的指示”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"950dcc4885","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：你是纪登奎，老朋友了","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"39592685e0","type":"paragraph","text":"刘建勋：他被关了四个月，换了四个月斗争。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"185b9d7fca","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：你说一点好处都没有吗？","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"b15f97c0b0","type":"paragraph","text":"纪登奎：大有好处。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"90d9b6578b","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：那是文敏生、赵文甫、何运洪他们搞的","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"d444619d0c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：（问王新同志）是什么时候到河南来的？","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"5140623912","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我上次路过郑州时，看到了一张大标语叫“大局已定，二七必胜”。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"f90f0397c3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：河南形势很好嘛。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"5bed1c190c","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到各地都站出了一些革命干部时）","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"b9cb628547","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这是何运洪干的好事！何运洪那么厉害呀！","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"af4c2581ca","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到要武装干部到北京集训时）","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"033573a452","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：集训也要去好人。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"41288732db","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到开封的情况，化肥厂主张打，我们主张不打，加强政治攻势时）","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"ae4fb2e819","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不讲厚房政策不好，要给八·二四做工作，我赞成你的意思。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"fde7cf8c69","type":"paragraph","text":"（当汇报到少数人不大讲政策，随便开枪，有时打死人时）","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"44fa2a1058","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：群众都起来议论，不赞成他们，群众起来反对，就收场了","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"fb0d36f5fd","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：抓军内一小振的口号搞不久，现在已经不那么香了，他们不拥军，一拥军就没有对象了！","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"dfe52b08c0","type":"paragraph","text":"王新：主要要从理论上把他们的错误思想批倒。","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"},{"id":"980cbf5892","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：对！","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95"}],"page":{"id":"e3654059cd","publicationId":"maoquanji50","articleId":"6c43859d95","start":87,"end":88}}}},"__N_SSG":true}